   Sergio and Davalos-Sotelo, Raymundo and Carlos Lopez-Acosta, Juan},
Title = {{Influence of Land-Use Changes (1993 and 2013) in the Distribution of
   Wild Edible Fruits From Veracruz (Mexico)}},
